  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_59",
    "english": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility.",
    "japanese": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility.",
    "korean": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility.",
    "chinese_simplified": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility.",
    "chinese_traditional": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility.",
    "spanish": "An artificial demon created anew with experimental data and cells of \"Saya,\" that remained in a research facility in Tokyo Kingdom and was acquired by the UFS.\n\nWhile \"Saya\" was capable of transforming between a human and an awakened form, the awakened form lacked stability. This is why Saya NEO was developed with no consideration for transformation between forms and designed purely for efficient operation as a biological weapon.\n\nThe details of what happened afterward are unclear, but records show that she escaped from the research facility."
  },
